    <string name="help_message">How to use:\n\n• Tap the card text to flip sides. After both sides are shown, the next tap shows the next card, tap on the left screen side shows first card side.\n• Learned/Unlearned/Delete: short tap toggles learned status based on the current list (in Not learned view -&gt; marks learned; in Learned view -&gt; marks not learned). Long press asks to delete the card.\n• Change Order switches which side is shown first.\n• Show learned toggles between learned and not learned cards.\n• Download cards icon on the top lets you import from a Google Drive/Sheets CSV link.\n• You can switch interface language (RU/EN button), show statistic (123 button), and change cards order mode sequential/random (SEQ/RND button).\n• You can add more sets of words (+ icon on the top right) and download new file with words.• Long press on the set button will suggest to delete the set. \n\n\nTip: long-press the card text to toggle debug info.</string>

